text: Agustín Alarcón Vargas (born 12 January 1962) is a Spanish rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==Notes== ==References== ==External links== * Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Spain Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Barakaldo
